article_id:844,category_name:News,title_name:A New Summon Showcase, Stirring Shadows (Part One), Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>A new Summon Showcase, Stirring Shadows (Part One), went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1572501600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers and dragons currently have boosted appearance rates.</div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured adventurer:</div><div>5★ Lathna (shadow/lance)</div><div><br></div><div>For information about other featured adventurers and dragons, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1572501600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1573538340"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons below, including a new adventurer and a dragon from the existing lineup.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
