			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A curious girl whose face often wears a somber<br>expression. She lost her family during a strange<br>incident at a library, and has been alone ever<br>since. Plagued with nightmares, she lives in fear<br>of something inside—the her that is not her.</li>
					</ul>
