				<span>Chaos Gift</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals shadow damage to the target<br>and nearby enemies. Poisoned foes<br>take extra damage. Continually tapping<br>the screen during the attack will unleash<br>additional blows, with up to a maximum of four.
				</div>
