			</dd>
	</dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/18a0c508eccb37dc48c820d6ec7c0f152.png"></span><span>The Faceless God II</span></dt><dd><div>When shapeshifting, Lathna will transform into<br>Nyarlathotep regardless of what dragon she is<br>equipped with. Grants an HP regen buff for<br>20 seconds each time she shapeshifts.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f1b1dac8108a7960100a7a9673e66f772.png"></span><span>Paralysis Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to paralysis by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f95daa91eaca6e0d41a23320398a9e792.png"></span><span>Dragon Time +20%</span></dt><dd><div>Extends shapeshift time by 20%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at maximum level with all mana circles unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured dragon:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
